channel.title: DPM patterns tutorials?
channel.description:
Hey, I've been looking for a while for a DPM tutorial on google n' stuff, but I can't seem get a straight answer on how to make one (and I know you can, I've seen [url='https://www.battlefront.com/resources/poc/_images/full/britain08.jpg']DPM[/url] textures on FPSbanana, but no one there wants to help, it seems). So, any idea, knowledge, obscure tutorial that might help me?
Thanks in advance (and sorry if this is in the wrong section).
